edu.nyu.cs.javagit.client.cli

Interface IParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CliGitAdd.GitAddParser, CliGitBranch.GitBranchParser, CliGitCheckout.GitCheckoutParser, CliGitClone.GitCloneParser, CliGitCommit.GitCommitParser, CliGitInit.GitInitParser, CliGitLog.GitLogParser, CliGitMv.GitMvParser, CliGitReset.GitResetParser, CliGitStatus.GitStatusParser

    public interface IParser
    IParser is an interface for parsing a git command line output stream. See how implementations of IParser are used in ProcessUtilities.
    See Also:
    ProcessUtilities
